{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "8e308b17-2abb-4ca2-806a-7fccdf6ca43d",
    "name": "store",
    "description": "This collection covers the full backend API for a store/e-commerce platform, running locally at http://127.0.0.1:8000/api. It provides endpoints for managing the entire lifecycle of a store — from user registration and authentication to product listings, orders, deliveries, and trader management. The API is organized into the following functional modules:\n\n- **Auth** — User registration, login, password reset, verification, and forgot-password flows.\n- **User** — Retrieve user orders and deliveries by user ID.\n- **Admin** — Admin-level access to fetch and manage platform users.\n- **Trader** — Trader registration, confirmation, product uploads, order and delivery tracking per trader.\n- **Products** — Create and retrieve products available in the store.\n- **Categories** — Manage product categories.\n- **Orders** — Create orders and retrieve them by ID or in bulk.\n- **Delivery** — Create and list delivery records.\n- **Offers** — Create product offers per trader and retrieve discounts by category.\n- **Coupon** — Create and list discount coupons tied to products.\n- **Banner** — Add and retrieve promotional banners linked to offers.\n- **Messages & Conversations** — Send messages, retrieve conversation history, and manage user conversations.\n- **Contact** — Submit and retrieve contact/support requests.\n- **Notifications** — Retrieve platform notifications.\n\nBase URL: `http://127.0.0.1:8000/api`  \nVariables used: `{{user_id}}`, `{{trader_id}}`, `{{order_id}}`, `{{product_id}}`, `{{offer_id}}`, `{{conv_id}}`, `{{category_id}}`, `{{admin_id}}`",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "42740215",
    "_collection_link": "https://go.postman.co/collection/42740215-8e308b17-2abb-4ca2-806a-7fccdf6ca43d?source=collection_link"
  },
